BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
a.  [`a_n = a_{n-1} + 4`] with [`a_1 = 5\text{.}`]
a.  [`a_n = 5 + 4(n-1)\text{.}`]
a.  Yes, since [`2013 = 5 + 4(503-1)`] (so [`a_{503} = 2013`]).

a.  133

a.  [`\frac{538\cdot 133}{2} = 35777\text{.}`]
a.  [`b_n = 1 + \frac{(4n+6)n}{2}\text{.}`]   

